{"tid":1436821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌曬你地老母，請將所有post焦點放番係五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:49:00.000Z","uid":101606,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"439f8b382b2e2ce1799c5edf2f1c4542cc7c34a2","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"由六月撐到宜家，你估係玩玩下？警察記者會好撚好笑？睇完記者撚人好撚爽？係咪爽完就精神式勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初走到宜家，靠既就係齊上齊落，不分化，點解呢家有咁多分化大台post呀，就係因為你地成撚日自我審查，呢樣野唔得個樣野唔得，剩係可以和理非鳩up一大輪。哦咁點先為知得呀？邊個決定呀？大台咪慢慢出現囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初既各有各做，齊上齊落去撚左邊，我睇完成個熱門都見唔到，大家既初衷去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n講多次，我地係光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n你話唔係革命？<br />\n<br />\n你睇下其中一個訴求：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">必不追究反送中抗爭者</span><br />\n<br />\n「佢地真係犯法，點樣唔拉呀」<br />\n<br />\n我地要討伐既就政府一言堂既以法而治，警察既選擇性執法，要拎番真正屬於香港既民主法治。係屬於每個香港市民既法治呀，唔係政府呀，係一場下而上既改革，唔係革命係咩。<br />\n<br />\n各位唔好幫自己兜，初衷係咩就係咩，如果連自己都唔敢講，你點感染到人地同你一齊做。只怕未拎到所謂民意，我地已經成一盤散沙。<br />\n<br />\n請大家集中番所有文宣行動post，停止推任何大台，分化，恥笑警狗post，因為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇撚用！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次唔係玩玩下，醒下吧，連登仔，香港人，今次一輸我地輸成世。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6b1823cec68bb9497ee2196010850e8934cb184","tid":1436821,"uid":36378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d8132065fef4327b638a077e96e93f84fcfa76","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85848489514efac437e0a4e1a8ca188da00907f9","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"推爆，順便屌曬所有廢post撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71012e26bfdc5f8ba9f9a69425eebe64698c4607","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"1b3a6c6babb9b16492f1aebcf7338fc7e601c2f4","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e56d1dc8a3c543c65f042cf32e8319d351ab27d0","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4c7d46d90f1728a0df9042b4c31c0ca5bb855319","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"cfa7fe01bc1a17cbe9a82c5a0d3deaf43f5e322b","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:17:19.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"02af89e2c5fea7586fa758c4d4819b698460815f","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"c0b97aa9f0e98aebd53c5af1e3b5309575768bed","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4533b5d7eaeef91f92906e3de913320a1c3cd4de","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e1bc9c49b949dcc8bdb347c68405ba3349a72db3","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"4b1d854b2c332f3f3c531c52622d228e0fe988db","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:30.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"92d3428f6a97fc18c0d85f71ed223061bd934d19","tid":1436821,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"